        If you're looking for information about someone detained in Creek County, you can search the jail roster online. Visit the Creek County Sheriff's Office website or call the jail directly at (918) 227-6371 during business hours. You can also contact Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000, and we'll help you locate your loved one and explain the bail options available.
