        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; color: var(--slate-700); line-height: 1.6;">
          Yes! Angel Bail Bonds accepts multiple payment methods for your convenience: Cash, Credit Cards, Zelle, and Venmo. This flexibility makes it easier to post bail quickly, even if you don't have cash on hand.
